Interface UserDataTranslator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AcceleratorTranslator, AltitudeTranslator, FuelTranslator, GPSTranslator, RPMTranslator, TempTranslator, VoltTranslator

    public interface UserDataTranslator
    Interface as a contract to all User data translation logic. All sensor (and in the future custom user data) should translate their values to human readable formats using this interface.

    hcpl
